We therefore manifeſt and delare our Deſires, to receive and believe all things contained in the ſacred Scriptures;
and by the knowledge of the Letter, to attain the ſpiritual ſenſe: and that alſo, not ſo much
in the ſingle diſcoveries appropriate to ſome peculiar matter, as in the entire and more comprehenſive evidences;
comparing Scripture with Scripture, thereby to come neereſt unto the minde of the Lord therein
revealed.
